    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感兴趣欢迎加QQ群1003184224~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《星径迷途》是一款关于”太空“和”星系“的休闲解谜游戏。在游戏中，你将对路径进行规划，释放关卡中所有尘封的星星，并收集遗失的星座。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >路径规划，收集星星</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关中，你只有一次发射小球的机会。小球会随着时间不断减速，并最终停止。你需要在小球停下来之前触碰所有尘封之匣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/2090a2a08b21c5da21e3f07038323641.poster.avif?t=1727326944\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/2090a2a08b21c5da21e3f07038323641.webm?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/2090a2a08b21c5da21e3f07038323641.mp4?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >导航器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用导航器可以为小球提供继续行进的动力，以及改变小球的行进方向。将导航器放置在正确的位置来进行路线规划。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/265ed28e503ca7233e57b76427424aa8.poster.avif?t=1727326944\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/265ed28e503ca7233e57b76427424aa8.webm?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/265ed28e503ca7233e57b76427424aa8.mp4?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的机制和挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一章都包含一个独特的机制，这些机制会让关卡环境发生微妙的变化，从而影响小球的行进路线。多多进行尝试，去认识、理解和利用这些机制吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/c436eb34c49663e58dc084c8ad42e4f4.poster.avif?t=1727326944\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/c436eb34c49663e58dc084c8ad42e4f4.webm?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/c436eb34c49663e58dc084c8ad42e4f4.mp4?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/f4200ddbd0af473e58c4ca924e2ce97f.poster.avif?t=1727326944\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/f4200ddbd0af473e58c4ca924e2ce97f.webm?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/f4200ddbd0af473e58c4ca924e2ce97f.mp4?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >见证星座重现于世</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关的星星们都构成一个独特的星座，并在通关后重现于世。努力通关，将星座全数收集吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/69f92fc01c24de503be683d34933d6b6.poster.avif?t=1727326944\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/69f92fc01c24de503be683d34933d6b6.webm?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164290/extras/69f92fc01c24de503be683d34933d6b6.mp4?t=1727326944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >绝对丰富的内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总共将有10个章节，每个章节都将引入一个新颖的机制。Demo将包含其中4个章节。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总共将有超过150个关卡。Demo将包含65个关卡。</p></li></ul>",
